title: In massive rejig, Jagan retains 11 ministers; 14 new faces in Andhra cabinet - Hindustan Times
content: In massive rejig, Jagan retains 11 ministers; 14 new faces in Andhra cabinet  Hindustan TimesView Full coverage on Google News
description: The list of the 25-member cabinet has been forwarded to Raj Bhavan for the approval of Governor Biswabhushan Harichandan. He will administer oath of office and secrecy to the new ministers at a grand ceremony on the lawns of the state secretariat at Velagapudi in Amaravati at 11.31 am on Monday.
